{"tid":118182,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"[文字遊戲] I found the love of my life.","createTime":"2017-02-12T20:52:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-08T15:03:39.000Z","uid":27741,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f98fe37be8f58fcfe639015d4992a346fdd83678","tid":118182,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T20:52:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">原汁原味 純粹分享</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>I found the love of my life. <br />\nShe didn't. <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nThere are two voices in our bedroom. <br />\nI knock.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWe&rsquo;re lying in bed. She&rsquo;s lying.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nI met the the most beautiful woman today. <br />\nShe said we have been married for 34 years.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nThey told me they could save either my wife or my son.<br />\nThey were wrong.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBrought roses home. <br />\nKeys didn't fit.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nI jumped. Then I regretted it.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFailed class and attempted suicide. Failed again.<br />\n</em></strong></div>"},{"pid":"80d2b66df5ece450c28a8e90dfe9c2df0404af85","tid":118182,"uid":47463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T21:00:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> lm"},{"pid":"781a1d8ab0f3df499941c9c799db1f49d25b3492","tid":118182,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T21:01:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> lm</blockquote><br />\n又係你啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3efe34ea1ec4f51d0662fea88750bc498ccae01","tid":118182,"uid":1675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T21:03:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfb5592588c31f9f71d6caff683144f6f3460448","tid":118182,"uid":1836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T21:07:33.000Z","msg":"好鍾意睇呢類post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaf7d11f71117cdd6e9c16ab826fab6ff1ea6c87","tid":118182,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T21:12:01.000Z","msg":"<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Smoking my very last cigarette. <br />\nAgain.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHer baby has Jame's eyes. And John's surname.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFound true love. Married someone else.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTurn me off. First thing said by the first sentient robot.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nThree months ago,<br />\nhe gave me a ring. <br />\nTwo days ago,<br />\nthe Army gave me a flag.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHe promised he would wait for her forever.<br />\nShe kept him to his word.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n9 months of excitement came to an end.<br />\nShe never cried.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Mama, I'm hungry.&quot;<br />\n&quot;I know sweetheart; maybe tomorrow.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;He&rsquo;s not coming, is he?&rdquo; I asked, squeezing my mother&rsquo;s hand, the multi-coloured party hat on my head slipping down. My mother squeezed back, and without a word walked back inside the house.<br />\n</em></div></strong>"},{"pid":"abed1fcf4d241413d1eadf5819c3c84b1954e6f3","tid":118182,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T21:13:54.000Z","msg":"Knock 係解敲門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢無加the door喎<br />\n有無其他意思"},{"pid":"d8582d55e7d8d9be9f9f8138cd74112bcb66bb88","tid":118182,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T21:15:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Knock 係解敲門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢無加the door喎<br />\n有無其他意思</blockquote><br />\n係敲門"},{"pid":"0d16ad055c1af423f6634e21af0aa9b686269b88","tid":118182,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T21:15:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好鍾意睇呢類post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4462f4ea52cf0c9fae2f228f58aaed24d826490c","tid":118182,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T21:16:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Knock 係解敲門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢無加the door喎<br />\n有無其他意思</blockquote><br />\n係敲門</blockquote><br />\n英文廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94ec6be6bc0501a28221ee5ee4345a471f24672f","tid":118182,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T21:28:56.000Z","msg":"<em><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>I threw away an opportunity because I was scared, now I&rsquo;m scared I will never have an opportunity.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nOne bullet is a lifetime supply.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMum taught me how to shave.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHe hit send, then a tree.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n'It's our fiftieth. Table for one.'<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWhat's your return policy on rings?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nShe went upstairs to check on her sleeping toddler. <br />\nThe bed was empty and the window was open.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</strong></div></em>"},{"pid":"7c6772a48cfdcde864126c38f702d2f35921bac6","tid":118182,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T21:30:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Knock 係解敲門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢無加the door喎<br />\n有無其他意思</blockquote><br />\n係敲門</blockquote><br />\